div.h2: Announcing the 2020 Union Star Agriculture Department Greenhouse Spring Plant Sale!!!

p.br: Due to COVID-19, we are changing things up this year. We are encouraging customers to shop through the use of our NEW Union Star Agriculture Department Greenhouse Website. All you will have to do is get online starting April 20th and go to https://my-site-100780-103479.square.site/ where you will choose your plants, select a pick up time, and place your order. Then all that is left is to come to the school greenhouse to pick up your order. If you would prefer you can always set up an appointment with Mr. Martin and purchase your plants that way. We are ONLY ALLOWING PEOPLE IN THE GREENHOUSE THAT HAVE AN APPOINTMENT FOR SHOPPING, with a limit of five people per appointment slot. See the flyer for more information on scheduling appointments.
